  <brief_title>Open Prospective Study for Determination of Predictive Measures for Pain During Colonoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Procedural Sequence in Same Day Consecutive Bidirectional Endoscopy Using Moderate Sedation: A Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
